1)  program to print sum of n factorial numbers.
---------------------------------------------------------------
def fact(n):
    if n==1:
        return 1
    else:
        return n*fact(n-1)
n=int(input('enter number'))
sum=0
for i in range (1,n+1):
    sum=sum+fact(i)
print (sum)
----------------------------------------------
Output:
enter number5
153
